ZrU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOfh70sceZrU&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1UYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=03fe70e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ofh70sceZrU</a><br />\n<br />\n應該係呢對夫婦"},{"pid":"ca78a4e772c20376e0c34e7c58af56de99cba860","tid":2290781,"uid":70301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f402aab945842ea89da647405ed82c8b2956bd9","tid":2290781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201118/MDPYWOJCT5BLFHZ7IGEUG5BBSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201118%2FMDPYWOJCT5BLFHZ7IGEUG5BBSU%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1UYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=e9e09dc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201118%2FMDPYWOJCT5BLFHZ7IGEUG5BBSU%2F&h=68ffccf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201118/MDPYWOJCT5BLFHZ7IGEUG5BBSU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n移民盤湧現 夫婦：劈到沽出為止<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】不少港人趕移民，二手放盤急增；有移民業主沽貨時雖表示仍看好香港樓市，並以貼市價放盤，但不諱言如能盡快成交「會減價」。<br />\n<br />\n10月經LOTR舉家移居英國的港媽Chloe，與丈夫育有兩子，坦言早有移民念頭，曾計劃移民加拿大或澳洲，但英國7月推出BNO新政策，旋即轉往英國。Chloe一家在港屬中產家庭，與丈夫每月收入共逾10萬元；出發前希望出售跑馬地東山臺翠壁低層兩房戶，實用面積609方呎，目前以市價1,080萬元放售。<br />\n<br />\n雖已帶備200萬元生活費前往英國，但Chloe擔心零收入下，費用不足應付一家四口所需；加上自住物業仍未沽出，或遭英國徵收資產增值稅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WNWWVbAU9__WWSVrWwetGagQI9c=/960x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EK3SWOAANVARNOXR5LZYBHX6BI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWNWWVbAU9__WWSVrWwetGagQI9c%3D%2F960x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEK3SWOAANVARNOXR5LZYBHX6BI.jpg&h=b648cd0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有經紀在樓盤廣告寫上「移民急讓」字眼作招徠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中原二手盤量飆44%<br />\n<br />\n單位起初開價1,100萬元，其後減價20萬至1,080萬元，丈夫曾建議劈價至沽出為止；當被問及心中最低價時，Chloe指1,000萬元或會接受，即較放盤價低約7%。由於疫情無法開放睇樓，10月出走後改為鎖匙盤，有信心可盡快套現。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑指，...........................。有代理指太古城目前最少20個「移民盤」，其中一名打算明年移居美國的業主，不惜連逾百萬元「SSD」辣稅放售物業，並提出售後租回條款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/51zfhGYfR5KpH3ShEnvdMDoNMFA=/1370x383/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RQPLKNKAFBF6DOI7SMKV5GFZFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F51zfhGYfR5KpH3ShEnvdMDoNMFA%3D%2F1370x383%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRQPLKNKAFBF6DOI7SMKV5GFZFM.jpg&h=44b6ada6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"第二個，業主移民大灣區？<br />\n<br />\n條友係咪忽撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ade583538bf24dbaaf037e54d83735006ae0a6","tid":2290781,"uid":196625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87dae43c9c0e71f909e4b5ffdf22423a2aebfe01","tid":2290781,"uid":249891,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3764efc5e9420eef9f9700233b51a8d0753dfe39","tid":2290781,"uid":196625,"like":121,"dislike":25,"score":96,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"55<br />\n<br />\n繼續減啦<br />\n減左我都唔要"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:37:21.000Z","msg":"遲下玩公屋可買賣 又重演私樓冧價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢又走唔到 人比你走到又點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"政府回血劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4693fe74546c9aa3ae84cd82a539199b0f4d4ab1","tid":2290781,"uid":39777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87dae43c9c0e71f909e4b5ffdf22423a2aebfe01","tid":2290781,"uid":249891,"like":6,